<!ELEMENT Kp (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT Climb (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT Startno (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT Tostart (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT Comments (#PCDATA)>
<!ATTLIST Comments
	lang CDATA "EST"
>
<!ELEMENT Startinterval (#PCDATA)>
<!ATTLIST Startinterval
