	startMethod (allocatTime | punching | limitedPunching | other) #IMPLIED
>
<!ELEMENT Race (Location, Date, Clock?, Note*, Contact*)>
<!ATTLIST Race
	id CDATA #IMPLIED
	distance (Classic | Short | Sprint | Long | Night | ShortClassic | Relay | Other) #IMPLIED
	resultform (Single | Multi | Qualification | Final | Series | CCup | Rogain | Other) #IMPLIED
