>
<!ELEMENT Accommodation (#PCDATA)>
<!ATTLIST Accommodation
	lang CDATA "EST"
>
<!ELEMENT Maps (#PCDATA)>
<!ATTLIST Maps
	lang CDATA "EST"
>
<!ELEMENT Driving (#PCDATA)>
